      "content": "🚀 Just discovered AI prompt engineering?\n\nHere's the #1 rule:\n\n❌ DON'T: \"Write a blog about marketing\"\n✅ DO: \"Write 500 words on email marketing for SaaS, targeting founders, in a conversational tone, including 3 actionable tips\"\n\nSpecificity = Quality output\n\n#AIPrompts #Productivity",
