      "platform": "twitter",
      "content": "💡 AI Tip of the Day:\n\nSave 2+ hours per week with this simple habit:\n\nBefore asking AI for help, spend 30 seconds writing:\n1️⃣ What you want (output format)\n2️⃣ Who it's for (audience)\n3️⃣ What tone (professional/casual/funny)\n4️⃣ Key points to cover\n\nYour results will improve 10x.\n\n#AITips #PromptEngineering",
