      "content": "⚡ The 3-Step AI Framework:\n\nStep 1: Context\n\"I'm a solopreneur with 5 hours/week for content...\"\n\nStep 2: Task\n\"Create a content calendar for 30 days...\"\n\nStep 3: Constraints\n\"Focus on LinkedIn, B2B audience, include hooks...\"\n\nThis simple structure will change how you use AI forever.\n\n#AIFramework #ContentCreation",
